      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical R2022 used under ISO 9001-compliant QMS. Version-controlled input decks maintained in FDA-internal repository. Regression test suite executed prior to each analysis campaign; all tests passed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
