      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification benchmarks demonstrate solver accuracy for beam-bending and contact problems relevant to construct geometry.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical verified against NAFEMS benchmark LE1 (plate bending) and Hertzian contact benchmark. Results within 1% of analytical solutions. No custom user elements employed."
